如果你想的话
If you want,

779
00:41:29,620 --> 00:41:32,300
我会把他打得皮开肉绽
I'll flay the flesh off the soles of his feet,

780
00:41:32,300 --> 00:41:34,880
然后帮你找印第安辣椒抹上去
and find you Indian pepper you can rub into the wound.

781
00:41:34,880 --> 00:41:36,830
这样不值一百美金吗
Isn't that a hundred dollar value?

782
00:41:36,830 --> 00:41:38,170
不值
No, it is not.

783
00:41:38,750 --> 00:41:41,580
既然我付了钱  你就应该服从我
When I have brought and paid for something, I will have my way.

784
00:41:41,590 --> 00:41:44,100
若不服从  为什么我要付你钱
Why do you think I'm paying you, if not to have my way.

785
00:41:44,100 --> 00:41:45,580
你现在要明白
It is time for you to learn.

786
00:41:45,590 --> 00:41:48,810
不是所有细节都能按照你的意愿走
You cannot have your way in every little particular.

787
00:41:48,810 --> 00:41:51,680
若你不满意
If you find I fail to satisfy your terms,

788
00:41:51,680 --> 00:41:54,840
等追捕结束后  我退你钱
I'll return your money at the end of this expedition.

789
00:41:54,840 --> 00:41:56,780
等我和小黑回去后
Little Blackie and I are ridding back to

790
00:41:56,780 --> 00:41:58,080
要把这些告诉警署  这是欺诈
the U.S. Marshal's office. This is fraud.

791
00:41:58,080 --> 00:41:59,090
该死的
God damn it!

792
00:41:59,090 --> 00:42:00,430
怎么了
What's going on?

793
00:42:00,430 --> 00:42:02,490
我们在谈生意
This is a business conversation.

794
00:42:02,490 --> 00:42:03,570
谈生意
Is that what you call it?

795
00:42:03,570 --> 00:42:06,340
看起来  你还是被小姑娘摆布
Sounds to me you're still being hoorawed by a little girl.

796
