They murdered women and children in Lawrence, Kansas.

805
00:42:24,500 --> 00:42:26,190
简直一派胡言
That's a God damn lie!

806
00:42:26,980 --> 00:42:28,790
你在哪儿服役
What army was you in, Mister?

807
00:42:28,790 --> 00:42:29,900
什里夫波特市
I was at Shreveport.

808
00:42:29,900 --> 00:42:31,660
先是跟着柯比・史密斯  然后
First with Kirby Smith, then with...

809
00:42:31,660 --> 00:42:33,430
从属哪个部队
What side was you on?

810
00:42:33,430 --> 00:42:35,610
北佛吉尼亚部队  考伯恩
I was in the army of Northern Virginia, Cogburn.

811
00:42:35,610 --> 00:42:37,540
