Our agreement is nullified.

820
00:42:58,290 --> 00:42:59,300
正合我意
That suits me.

821
00:42:59,920 --> 00:43:01,420
分道扬镳  自力更生吧
It's man for himself.

822
00:43:01,420 --> 00:43:03,070
恭喜你  考伯恩
Congratulations, Cogburn.

823
00:43:03,920 --> 00:43:06,490
