You've graduated from marauder to wetnurse.

824
00:43:08,960 --> 00:43:10,540
再见
A-dios.

825
00:43:16,490 --> 00:43:18,980
我们不需要他  是吧  警官
We don't need him, do we Marshal?

826
00:43:21,510 --> 00:43:23,490
会需要他的夏普斯卡宾枪吧
We'll miss his Sharps carbine.

827
00:43:24,000 --> 00:43:27,230
