Go on.

830
00:44:01,560 --> 00:44:02,970
待在这儿  小妹妹
Stay here, sister.

831
00:44:03,130 --> 00:44:04,760
我去见巴格比
And I will see Bagby.

832
00:44:27,000 --> 00:44:28,480
切尼来过吗
Has Chaney been here?

833
00:44:28,490 --> 00:44:29,680
没有
No.

834
